'''George Ellis''' is a man Amelia went on a blind date with.

==History==
George went on a date with Amelia. During their date, he got a phone call from his ex-wife. He told Amelia his ex-wife tells him he loves him when she drinks.

==Relationships==
===Romantic===
====Ex-Wife====
He is divorced, but still hung up on his ex-wife, who contacts him regularly.

====[[Amelia Shepherd]]====
He went on one date with Amelia. It didn't go well because he talked about his ex-wife.

==Notes and Trivia==
*Violet set him and Amelia up, thinking he was over his ex-wife.
